Kung hindi,

00:22:21.070 --> 00:22:21.920
gaano katagal ito aabutin

00:22:21.920 --> 00:22:23.170
hanggang sa kaya kitang protektahan

00:22:24.110 --> 00:22:25.100
at pakasalan ka?

